## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on innovation classification systems. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English publications. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of innovation means that new classification systems and theories may emerge beyond the scope of this report.